{"tid":2311489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"內蒙招300漢語教師 加速滅母語","createTime":"2020-12-04T05:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T06:57:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d0b2dba1e64f97753365119a41a1a7652812a961","tid":2311489,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T05:59:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201203/NIGVP43VWBEXBKWXHPWUJCPFN4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201203%2FNIGVP43VWBEXBKWXHPWUJCPFN4%2F&d=my%2BdBOIpGqNKE9iEaZHJGLyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=acbe04e5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201203%2FNIGVP43VWBEXBKWXHPWUJCPFN4%2F&h=3f0a6247\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201203/NIGVP43VWBEXBKWXHPWUJCPFN4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n內蒙招300漢語教師 加速滅母語<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EyjSjWZ0bMX3Kpmg8otPrfWgk1g=/1585x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZTLJXGWUMVCDVPKNDGZJYHUHZ4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEyjSjWZ0bMX3Kpmg8otPrfWgk1g%3D%2F1585x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZTLJXGWUMVCDVPKNDGZJYHUHZ4.jpg&h=18224a88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■強推漢語曾引起蒙族人群起反抗。<br />\n<br />\n內蒙教育部9月在。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n須提供思想品德證明<br />\n<br />\n內蒙古自治區教育廳、財政廳等四個部門近日聯合下發文件《關於加強民族語言授課學校國家統編教材師資隊伍建設的若干措施》，計劃在全國招聘300名「特設崗位教師」，應聘者須為35歲以下，擁有本科及以上學歴，提供就讀學校出具的「思想品德」證明。旅居日本的蒙裔教授楊海英表示，當局此舉是為了進一步消除蒙古族母語教育，「它面向全國招生，等於不在內蒙古招聘，肯定招的都是漢人。到了內蒙古之後取代蒙古人老師，進一步加強同化政策。」<br />\n<br />\n今年8月，內蒙傳出當局要求當地小學、初中一年級學生部份原本以蒙語授課的科目，在新學年改為以漢語授課，引來大批蒙古族學生和家長罷課和集會，當局強力打壓，拘捕過千人，據報至少70人至今依然音訊全無。<br />\n<br />\n自由亞洲電台"},{"pid":"c2259c15a25e6422e2f8a1f33970b09a85d3e2df","tid":2311489,"uid":115579,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cited